{'relation': ['https://d-scholarship.pitt.edu/48495/', 'https://cesf.pitt.edu'], 'title': ['Exploring the associations between future orientation and mental health outcomes among youth impacted by community violence'], 'creator': ['Klotz, Sarah', 'Culyba, Alison', 'Riley, Alec', 'Ajith, Aniruddh', 'Wilson, Tyia', 'Sierra, Emily', 'Fabio, Tony'], 'description': ['Community violence disproportionately affects youth residing in neighborhoods impacted by structural inequities and increases risk for mental health symptoms, including anxiety, depression, and post-traumatic stress. Future orientation—the way young people perceive and plan for their future—can serve as a protective factor, fostering resilience in the context of violence exposure. Through community-partnered, interdisciplinary research, we aim to identify pathways that strengthen youth resilience and inform community-driven interventions. In partnership with youth-serving organizations in Pittsburgh, this study utilizes a cross-sectional social network survey to examine relationships between violence exposure and mental health outcomes among youth ages 13-19. We additionally explore the potential buffering effect of future orientation on mental health outcomes among those who have experienced violence. This work underscores the need for engaged scholarship that bridges research and practice to promote long-term well-being among youth residing in communities affected by violence.'], 'date': ['2025-03-04'], 'type': ['Conference or Workshop Item', 'NonPeerReviewed'], 'format': ['application/pdf'], 'language': ['en'], 'rights': [None], 'identifier': ['https://d-scholarship.pitt.edu/48495/1/Klotz_CESF%20Poster_FINAL_v2.pdf', '  Klotz, Sarah and Culyba, Alison and Riley, Alec and Ajith, Aniruddh and Wilson, Tyia and Sierra, Emily and Fabio, Tony  (2025) Exploring the associations between future orientation and mental health outcomes among youth impacted by community violence.  In: 2025 Community Engaged Scholarship Forum, 2025-03-04, University of Pittsburgh.    (Unpublished)  ']}